Exe 1
Write a function that inputs sides of rectangle from the keyboard to calculate area of a rectangle using pointers.

Exe 2
Write a function that inputs two strings from the keyboard to swap them using pointers. 

Exe 3
Write a program to dynamically allocate an integer, a character and a string, assign a value to them 
and print out their values.
(Hint: use new and delete operators to declare variables)